Class DefaultBWListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • bwapi.DefaultBWListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BWEventListener

    public class DefaultBWListener
extends Object
implements BWEventListener
    Convenience class that extends all methods in BWEventListener. Not all of the methods need an implementation.
